<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 22:07:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，最新的停火提议排除了以色列在埃及-加沙边境的永久存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-latest-deal-proposal-excludes-permanent-israeli-presence-on-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-85e7-dd90-a7d1-cfffd2a10000</link><description>该计划将允许内塔尼亚胡宣布以色列将继续留在费城路线，直到找到替代方案。 预计埃及会将这一版本交给已宣布参加开罗峰会的哈马斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 20:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-latest-deal-proposal-excludes-permanent-israeli-presence-on-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-85e7-dd90-a7d1-cfffd2a10000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯兰国声称对德国造成三人死亡的袭击负责：“为巴勒斯坦穆斯林报仇”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-24/ty-article/islamic-state-claims-attack-in-germany-that-killed-three-to-avenge-muslims-in-palestine/00000191-85de-d79a-a9fd-e5ff824a0000</link><description>警方表示，袭击者在斯洛尼根的一个节日上割断了多人的喉咙，造成三人死亡、至少八人受伤，其中四人伤势严重。伊斯兰国声称对此负责，称其目的是“为巴勒斯坦和世界各地的穆斯林报仇”</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 19:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-24/ty-article/islamic-state-claims-attack-in-germany-that-killed-three-to-avenge-muslims-in-palestine/00000191-85de-d79a-a9fd-e5ff824a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，三名以色列预备役士兵在加沙地带中部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-battle-in-the-central-gaza-strip-idf-announces/00000191-859e-d79a-a9fd-e5ff97cc0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布中士。丹尼尔·佩切纽克 (Danil Pechenyuk) 少校，26 岁，中士。尼泰·梅托迪 (Nitai Metodi) 少校，23 岁，周五在加沙城 Zeitoun 社区发生的爆炸中丧生。在另一起事件中，中士。亚尼夫·伊扎克·奥伦 (Yaniv Itzhak Oren) 少校，35 岁，在加沙中部的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 19:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-battle-in-the-central-gaza-strip-idf-announces/00000191-859e-d79a-a9fd-e5ff97cc0000</guid></item><item><title>蒙面以色列定居者在不同事件中袭击了巴勒斯坦西岸的两个村庄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-settlers-attack-two-palestinian-west-bank-villages-in-separate-incidents/00000191-8560-d03f-a1bd-ff6d4f0f0000</link><description>周六，蒙面定居者在巴勒斯坦西岸村庄发动袭击，造成至少两人受伤并损坏财产。截至周六晚上，尚未逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 18:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-settlers-attack-two-palestinian-west-bank-villages-in-separate-incidents/00000191-8560-d03f-a1bd-ff6d4f0f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 323 天：哈马斯代表团前往开罗了解谈判最新情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-323-hamas-delegation-heads-to-cairo-for-update-on-negotiations/00000191-8518-d179-a995-cd78664b0000</link><description>哈马斯代表团将抵达开罗，了解停火/人质谈判的最新情况；哈马斯：并不意味着他们会参加会谈 ■ 周日的峰会包括中央情报局局长、美国中东问题特使布雷特·麦格克、卡塔尔总理、埃及情报部门负责人以及以色列情报部门负责人 ■ 黎巴嫩从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了 100 多枚火箭弹 ■以色列国防军：部队在拉法加沙市打死数十名恐怖分子 ■ 法国犹太教堂附近疑似纵火袭击中警官受伤 ■ 战争进入 323 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 17:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-323-hamas-delegation-heads-to-cairo-for-update-on-negotiations/00000191-8518-d179-a995-cd78664b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生部称，周六加沙有近 70 人死亡、200 多人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/close-to-70-killed-over-200-wounded-in-gaza-on-saturday-gaza-health-ministry-says/00000191-851c-d03f-a1bd-ff3db4eb0000</link><description>以色列军队撤出加沙南部城市哈马德的某些地区后，卫生官员发现了数十具尸体。返回的居民回忆道：“什么都没有，没有公寓，没有家具，没有房屋，只有破坏”</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:43:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/close-to-70-killed-over-200-wounded-in-gaza-on-saturday-gaza-health-ministry-says/00000191-851c-d03f-a1bd-ff3db4eb0000</guid></item><item><title>开罗峰会前夕，以色列呼吁内塔尼亚胡达成停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-cairo-summit-israelis-call-for-netanyahu-to-make-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-84ac-d179-a995-cdec7abd0000</link><description>“看来这是最后的机会了。人质的母亲说，要么达成协议，要么事态升级。人质被绑架到加沙十多个月后，每周都有抗议活动敦促达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-cairo-summit-israelis-call-for-netanyahu-to-make-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-84ac-d179-a995-cdec7abd0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官呼吁对以色列和哈马斯官员的逮捕令做出紧急裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-for-urgent-ruling-on-arrest-warrants-for-israeli-and-hamas-officials/00000191-848c-d632-add9-b5ffd64e0000</link><description>在一份法庭文件中，检察官卡里姆·汗敦促法官就他对以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡、哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔等人发出逮捕令的请求做出裁决</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 14:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-for-urgent-ruling-on-arrest-warrants-for-israeli-and-hamas-officials/00000191-848c-d632-add9-b5ffd64e0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫因厄立特里亚政治发生争吵，两名厄立特里亚人死亡，多人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/two-eritreans-killed-multiple-wounded-in-tel-aviv-brawl-over-eritrean-politics/00000191-848a-dcc6-a5bf-b5cf57950000</link><description>据称，袭击者刺伤多人，并向教堂投掷催泪瓦斯，造成包括儿童在内的多名成员受伤。特拉维夫警察局长称这种情况“不可接受”，并呼吁将袭击者驱逐出境</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 14:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/two-eritreans-killed-multiple-wounded-in-tel-aviv-brawl-over-eritrean-politics/00000191-848a-dcc6-a5bf-b5cf57950000</guid></item><item><title>周五从黎巴嫩向以色列发射100多枚火箭弹，两栋房屋遭到直接击中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/over-100-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-at-israel-on-friday-two-houses-suffer-direct-hit/00000191-8348-d445-a39f-dfe9f4ab0000</link><description>周五，以色列北部多处地点因黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹而起火 ■ 以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩的多个目标，造成至少七名真主党特工死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 07:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/over-100-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-at-israel-on-friday-two-houses-suffer-direct-hit/00000191-8348-d445-a39f-dfe9f4ab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，三名以色列预备役士兵在加沙地带中部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article-live/rockets-from-lebanon-hit-two-homes-in-northern-israeli-city-of-kiryat-shmona/00000191-8250-d00c-a7fd-b656dcb70005</link><description>哈马斯卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 40,334 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀。 ■ 以摩萨德负责人为首的以色列代表团将于周日前往开罗参加停火谈判。 ■ 美国高级将领未经宣布进行中东之行，将于下周 ■ 以色列国防军呼吁加沙地带中部几个街区的居民撤离 ■ 法国警方正在搜寻涉嫌纵火袭击犹太教堂的嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 03:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article-live/rockets-from-lebanon-hit-two-homes-in-northern-israeli-city-of-kiryat-shmona/00000191-8250-d00c-a7fd-b656dcb70005</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦青少年在下班时被以色列狙击手射杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-getting-off-work-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper/00000191-811e-d03f-a1bd-fb3f86330000</link><description>沙迪正在他父亲的洗车场工作，一群年轻人开始从附近的校园向边境警察投掷燃烧弹。一名狙击手从远处向他们开枪，未击中并杀死了沙迪</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 22:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-getting-off-work-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper/00000191-811e-d03f-a1bd-fb3f86330000</guid></item><item><title>仅有海峡还不够：伊朗希望用新型无人机航母出海</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/the-straits-are-not-enough-iran-wants-to-take-to-the-oceans-with-a-new-drone-carrier/00000191-7e84-d8d0-a7bb-ffa570590000</link><description>伊朗在中东培养真主党和其他傀儡民兵，使其能够控制对全球贸易至关重要的关键水道。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 19:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/the-straits-are-not-enough-iran-wants-to-take-to-the-oceans-with-a-new-drone-carrier/00000191-7e84-d8d0-a7bb-ffa570590000</guid></item><item><title>前人质会见内塔尼亚胡：我告诉他他应对10月7日事件负责，他的妻子指责军队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostage-met-netanyahu-i-told-him-hes-responsible-for-oct-7-his-wife-blamed-the-army/00000191-8059-d00c-a7fd-b65fd89a0000</link><description>与内塔尼亚胡总理及其妻子会面的一位与会者表示，她问他们为什么不呼吁以色列人从哈马斯的囚禁中获释</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 18:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostage-met-netanyahu-i-told-him-hes-responsible-for-oct-7-his-wife-blamed-the-army/00000191-8059-d00c-a7fd-b65fd89a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 322 天：美国表示，关于停战谈判接近崩溃的报道是不准确的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-322-reports-that-truce-talks-are-near-collapse-inaccurate-u-s-says/00000191-8013-d371-a3d9-9fd3d8250001</link><description>美国、卡塔尔和埃及致力于确保周日在开罗举行的峰会，以达成以色列和哈马斯之间的人质/停火协议 ■ 埃及、卡塔尔将向哈马斯提交以色列关于费城路线和拉法过境点的新提案，这是停战谈判的一个症结所在■ Shin Bet 负责人 Ronen Bar 警告总理，约旦河西岸的犹太恐怖主义正在危及以色列的生存 ■ 战争进入 322 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 17:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-322-reports-that-truce-talks-are-near-collapse-inaccurate-u-s-says/00000191-8013-d371-a3d9-9fd3d8250001</guid></item><item><title>由于对内塔尼亚胡政治化的担忧，以色列赫尔佐格建议他监督国营的 10 月 7 日守夜活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-herzog-suggests-he-lead-oct-7-vigil-amid-concerns-of-netanyahu-politicization/00000191-7f5b-daab-a3f3-ffdb0dd50000</link><description>以色列总统赫尔佐格向内塔尼亚胡建议，他的办公室将监督哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击一周年纪念活动，公众对人质家庭和加沙边境社区所称的国营活动政治化表示强烈反对</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 16:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-herzog-suggests-he-lead-oct-7-vigil-amid-concerns-of-netanyahu-politicization/00000191-7f5b-daab-a3f3-ffdb0dd50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙中部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-7fd0-d741-a9d5-7ffbe00c0000</link><description>中士。一等兵（后）Evyatar Atuar，一名来自罗什艾因的 24 岁男子，于周五在加沙中部被杀 ■​​ 在同一事件中七名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:41:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-7fd0-d741-a9d5-7ffbe00c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列律师协会撤销针对阿拉伯以色列律师关于加沙战争观点的听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-bar-association-drops-hearing-against-arab-israeli-lawyer-over-gaza-war-views/00000191-7f07-d06e-afdd-7f978ed80000</link><description>一名右翼活动人士因该律师在社交媒体上发帖抨击加沙战争并将极右翼部长本-格维尔称为“恐怖分子”而对他提出投诉，以色列律师协会决定取消针对他的纪律听证会</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-bar-association-drops-hearing-against-arab-israeli-lawyer-over-gaza-war-views/00000191-7f07-d06e-afdd-7f978ed80000</guid></item><item><title>人质面临死亡，以色列国防部长必须发声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/with-the-hostages-facing-death-israels-defense-chiefs-must-speak-out/00000191-7ece-dee7-a9d1-ffef9aea0000</link><description>尽管他们可能付出代价，但在某些时候，将军们需要在与哈马斯达成协议、定居者暴力以及征召极端正统派入伍等问题上打破沉默。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 11:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/with-the-hostages-facing-death-israels-defense-chiefs-must-speak-out/00000191-7ece-dee7-a9d1-ffef9aea0000</guid></item><item><title>为了削弱内塔尼亚胡并保护其经济，伊朗正在权衡以色列袭击的时机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/in-bid-to-undermine-netanyahu-and-spare-its-economy-iran-weighs-timing-of-israel-attack/00000191-7e0f-d2f8-adf1-7e0fd0f10000</link><description>自哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚被暗杀以来已经过去了很长一段时间，加上革命卫队声明“时间站在我们一边”，这引发了西方的猜测，即伊朗不打算很快对以色列进行报复</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:21:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/in-bid-to-undermine-netanyahu-and-spare-its-economy-iran-weighs-timing-of-israel-attack/00000191-7e0f-d2f8-adf1-7e0fd0f10000</guid></item></channel></rss>